Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.50,0:00:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.53,0:00:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧，那裡面會有要塞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.33,0:00:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天城博士，我們到達了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.37,0:00:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,類似目標的雲層了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.64,0:00:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣闖進去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.97,0:00:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,講的真簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.78,0:00:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女人就是膽量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.86,0:00:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這...這是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.29,0:00:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是ACADEMY?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.67,0:00:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.66,0:02:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家好好跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.73,0:02:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.01,0:02:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她們走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.58,0:02:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們一定帶救援回來的，請保重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.32,0:02:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以從這裡進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.63,0:03:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.83,0:03:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.13,0:03:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.44,0:03:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人 主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.04,0:03:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仲人先生  等等 你們二個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.14,0:03:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像有可疑...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.68,0:03:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡鈴加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.25,0:04:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人   主人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.15,0:04:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.52,0:04:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美 沙希  卡鈴加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.69,0:04:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.56,0:04:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見不了，天城博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.44,0:04:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布籣度傅士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.24,0:04:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還是那麼勇敢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.07,0:04:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到你竟然帶著鋼鐵天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.34,0:04:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闖入這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.78,0:04:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我早就己經覺悟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.65,0:04:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們抓仲人，到底想做甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.98,0:04:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是成熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.89,0:04:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為你會馬上叫出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.49,0:04:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另一個人的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.02,0:04:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧?綾小路博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.29,0:04:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從那時候一直昏迷到現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.27,0:04:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.87,0:04:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他現在在治療室等待回復中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.11,0:04:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到時候應該可以見面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.14,0:05:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在，我希望你聽我們講
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.15,0:05:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓你明白事情的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.15,0:05:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真相?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.89,0:05:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭，我卡鈴加的攻擊無效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.10,0:05:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.07,0:05:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是陷阱      陷阱?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.53,0:05:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們知道我們會來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.27,0:05:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在講這些也沒有用啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.74,0:05:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要儘早把仲人先生給救出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.81,0:05:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道，總之你要鎮定下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.95,0:05:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能鎮定呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.05,0:05:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣胡亂敲打，只會浪費能源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.22,0:05:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要靜下心來，利用敲擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.69,0:05:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣可以由聲音聽出哪裡最薄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.23,0:05:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個聲音...    姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.38,0:06:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.95,0:06:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...現在...馬上過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.76,0:06:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把天城博士帶來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.57,0:06:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎，天城博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.94,0:06:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是這ACADEMY
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.74,0:06:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最高的執行者，咸路斯基
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.51,0:06:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,威路斯基
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.28,0:06:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請坐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.32,0:06:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想告訴我的真相，到底是甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.42,0:06:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們所居住的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.56,0:06:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對你們來講應該是未來的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.36,0:07:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利用最強的科學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.40,0:07:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,創造出最舒適的生活環境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.50,0:07:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每個人都可以過著和平幸 生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.44,0:07:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時突然有敵人突擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.37,0:07:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我們做攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.48,0:07:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種力量是我們所理解外的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.02,0:07:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果讓世界再次陷入危機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.02,0:07:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些謎樣的力量，我們稱為魔族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.26,0:07:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,普通武器對他們無效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.07,0:07:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們利用科學與咒術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.80,0:07:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開發了擁有天使程式的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.91,0:07:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ANGELHEART
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.51,0:07:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,創造出了鋼鐵天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.28,0:07:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是在眾多的魔族面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.68,0:07:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鋼鐵天使並無法發揮出全部力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.19,0:07:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得缺少甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.96,0:08:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果是缺少術者的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.63,0:08:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被封印在ANGEL
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.10,0:08:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,HEART裡面的天使的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.03,0:08:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓它完全發揮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.23,0:08:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要最棒最優秀的術者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.50,0:08:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是對未來來講，術者太少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.17,0:08:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現存的術者力量也不夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.91,0:08:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們才會來到這個時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.12,0:08:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找出優秀的術者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.12,0:08:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將咒術延傳到未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.25,0:08:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，有一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.42,0:08:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對這個理論大力反對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.73,0:08:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他認為就算我們找到這個時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.96,0:08:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最優秀的術者帶回我們的時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.60,0:08:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也無法戰勝魔族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.73,0:08:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有ANGEL
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.10,0:08:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,HEART的許可，是沒用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.57,0:08:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以他就製造出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.44,0:08:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ANGELHEART.改
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.71,0:08:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將全人類的敵人惡魔的本，性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.78,0:08:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與天使的本，性一起封印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.82,0:09:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身為科學者的你，應該了解吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.82,0:09:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將未知的力量，當作武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.23,0:09:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是多危險的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.10,0:09:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道那科學家...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.17,0:09:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對，就是綾小路博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.40,0:09:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能! 對人類來講
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.34,0:09:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那危險的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.64,0:09:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾小路博士怎麼可能會去製造呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.71,0:09:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在可以阻止久留美的只有仲人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.05,0:09:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你也去勸勸仲人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.85,0:09:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在久留美變成惡魔之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.19,0:09:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必須把ANGELHEART
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.39,0:09:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改給停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.50,0:09:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界的命運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.97,0:09:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掌握在ANGELHEART
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.54,0:09:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改的手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.41,0:09:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有那唯一可以控制擁有改的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.28,0:10:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鋼鐵天使那個優秀的術者的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.45,0:10:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你考慮清楚了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.47,0:10:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，綾小路博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.34,0:10:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.80,0:10:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暫時先給你們獨處吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.31,0:10:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.38,0:10:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人主人主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.29,0:10:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人，我現在來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.90,0:10:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓開!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.44,0:11:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人，主人在哪兒?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.48,0:11:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會告訴你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.02,0:11:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪裡? 主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.25,0:11:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美在叫你 久留美在叫你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.89,0:11:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.26,0:11:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你終於明白了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.43,0:11:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.97,0:11:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一件事，我可以辦得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.34,0:11:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是相信久留美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.17,0:11:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仲人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.18,0:11:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.85,0:11:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你繼續前進的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.72,0:11:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美，你還是乖乖聽話吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.22,0:11:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放開我，久留美要去主人身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.96,0:11:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想做甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.93,0:12:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，已經沒有時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.00,0:12:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.23,0:12:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我真正的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.57,0:12:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「突入! ACADEMY基地」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.26,0:14:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊~主人和彌海兒KISS了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.86,0:14:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別誤會了，久留美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.23,0:14:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你繼續看下去就會了解我的心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.23,0:14:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,次回 鋼鐵天使久留美第20話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.67,0:14:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「終極的超鋼鐵天使」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.54,0:14:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我繼續看唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.81,0:14:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?久留美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.11,0:14:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才看電視
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.41,0:14:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正好看到主人和彌海兒KISS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.22,0:14:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不...那是對方自己過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.45,0:14:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到主人有那種興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.95,0:14:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的，久留美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.59,0:14:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你繼續看下去就會了解我的心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.33,0:14:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,次回 鋼鐵天使久留美第20話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.13,0:14:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「終極的超鋼鐵天使」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.36,0:14:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看了就會明白了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.01,0:15:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請保持室內光亮，別太近看唷
